### TPS API - Workflow 테스트
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8089/api/v1

### 테스트용 변수
@testProjectId = [생성된_프로젝트_ID로_교체]

################################################################################
### [Workflow API] 워크플로우 생성/수정/삭제
################################################################################

### 테스트 1: 기본 워크플로우 생성 (7단계)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/project/{{testProjectId}}/default
Content-Type: application/json

### 테스트 2: 커스텀 워크플로우 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": "{{testProjectId}}",
  "name": "Simple Workflow",
  "description": "TODO → IN_PROGRESS → DONE",
  "nodesJson": "[{\"id\": \"todo\", \"type\": \"stage\", \"label\": \"To Do\"}, {\"id\": \"in_progress\", \"type\": \"stage\", \"label\": \"In Progress\"}, {\"id\": \"done\", \"type\": \"stage\", \"label\": \"Done\"}]",
  "edgesJson": "[{\"from\": \"todo\", \"to\": \"in_progress\"}, {\"from\": \"in_progress\", \"to\": \"done\"}]",
  "isDefault": false
}

### 테스트 3: 워크플로우 조회
@workflowId = [생성된_워크플로우_ID로_교체]
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/{{workflowId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 테스트 4: 프로젝트별 워크플로우 목록
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/project/{{testProjectId}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 테스트 5: 상태별 워크플로우 목록 (ACTIVE)
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/project/{{testProjectId}}/status/ACTIVE
Content-Type: application/json

### 테스트 6: 상태별 워크플로우 목록 (DRAFT)
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/project/{{testProjectId}}/status/DRAFT
Content-Type: application/json

### 테스트 7: 기본 워크플로우 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/project/{{testProjectId}}/default
Content-Type: application/json

### 테스트 8: 워크플로우 수정 (DRAFT 상태만 가능)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workflows/{{workflowId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Simple Workflow Updated",
  "description": "TODO → IN_PROGRESS → REVIEW → DONE",
  "nodesJson": "[{\"id\": \"todo\", \"type\": \"stage\", \"label\": \"To Do\"}, {\"id\": \"in_progress\", \"type\": \"stage\", \"label\": \"In Progress\"}, {\"id\": \"review\", \"type\": \"stage\", \"label\": \"Review\"}, {\"id\": \"done\", \"type\": \"stage\", \"label\": \"Done\"}]",
  "edgesJson": "[{\"from\": \"todo\", \"to\": \"in_progress\"}, {\"from\": \"in_progress\", \"to\": \"review\"}, {\"from\": \"review\", \"to\": \"done\"}]"
}

### 테스트 9: 워크플로우 발행 (DRAFT → ACTIVE)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/{{workflowId}}/publish
Content-Type: application/json

### 테스트 10: 기본 워크플로우로 설정
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/{{workflowId}}/set-default
Content-Type: application/json

### 테스트 11: 워크플로우 보관
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows/{{workflowId}}/archive
Content-Type: application/json

### 테스트 12: 워크플로우 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/workflows/{{workflowId}}
Content-Type: application/json

################################################################################
### 에러 케이스
################################################################################

### 에러 1: 필수 필드 누락 (projectId)
POST {{baseUrl}}/workflows
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Workflow"
}

### 에러 2: ACTIVE 워크플로우 수정 시도
PUT {{baseUrl}}/workflows/[active_workflow_id]
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Cannot Update Active Workflow"
}

### 에러 3: 기본 워크플로우 삭제 시도
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/workflows/[default_workflow_id]
Content-Type: application/json

### 에러 4: 존재하지 않는 워크플로우 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/workflows/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Content-Type: application/json
